divs: Sighting DetailsWhen looking through the window of my house I observed a strange cloud over the city of Porto Alegre. The image was blurred and strange. I took two photos of the sighting. After analysis on my PC I was curious about what I observed. I used a Photo editing software and after reduce glare and increase contrast a strange shape appeared bright.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Canoas
This sighting has never been favorited.
